{
  "text": "Several papers analyze the climatology of synopticscale systems over the Mediterranean [CITATION_1] ,b, Trigo et al. 1999 . Other papers describe the averaged geopotential height fields relevant for the main modes of Mediterranean and European precipitation [CITATION_2] . The climatology of moisture transports, precipitation, evaporation and fresh water input into the Mediterranean has been reported by [CITATION_3] . They also analyze the impact of the NAO in the freshwater flux into the Mediterranean.",
